title: After tragedy, Oklahoma State rolls past Kansas 58-10
text:

Oklahoma State players and staff form a prayer circle prior to an NCAA college football game between Kansas and Oklahoma St in Stillwater, Okla., Saturday, Oct. 24, 2015. Earlier in the day tragedy struck at the Oklahoma State homecoming parade as a car ran into a group of parade watchers killing at least three and injuring dozens more.
